normalised: Pathaay pharamani bigyan ni ma gabi gang jorao, ahng jomao gonaani scholarship ni portal khou nongi mona ni bagai sawai monoi. Bharotni gabang pathaa ni dongmon nongi, anaha anom anao, gabang goham ni bagai kasta jang jonaoi lagoi. Mumbai ni Rohan nikhri gorab bibaswri anjam I I T hao sonai hamoi dongbana, honab.

Gabang gusong scholarship ni portal dong, anaha, gom lakhinai ya gongwona. Gabang anom dongmon mona ni saajaa bibaswri gaoi, gonaani platform har aaga ni ronsai bikhoi. Khanaab, bikhana kharngra ni khitha-metha khou nina lakhigora.

Gusong portal har ni bikhana kharngra ni portal Buddy for Study, Vidyalakshmi (Bharot sorkar ni ahnkhra), ar Scholarship dot net. Be platform har gabang jayga ni bikhana kharngra khou anjoroi — sorkar ni okhor har, gyouma langni har, ar N G O har. Be har bidyarthi har khou pathaay ni gorob, jati, goham ni dongmon, ar pathaay ni gona (bekhri, Computer Science ni B.Tech ongou M B B S) ni gami filter honoi.

Gonaani bikhana kharngra ni gami, Tata Institute of Fundamental Research (T I F R) ongou gonaani montri mool ni website har khou ninagora. Khanaab, som bakhra ni sima ya gongwona – imagine honagora three Idiots’ Raju engineering exam khou dongsri dongonai ni bagai sonoi lakhidongonai nikhri! Khanaab, aaga simana apply honagora. Be gabei gabei scholarship ni gabei gabei gorob lakhingni niyam dongoi.
Fainal lao, “hwi hwi” portal ya gabei gabei mansi ni gonaani profile ar nongi ni gami gonaoi. Som lakhinaoi gabang khou nina ar gonaani ar goudain jith khou khanaab honoi bibaswri gaoi thakhia.
